<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Young Africans Technology</title>
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: capitalize;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        color: #2c3145;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .section-title-border {
        background-color: #000;
        height: 3px;
        width: 44px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
      }
      .text-custom {
        color: #00bd2a;
      }
      .text-muted {
        color: #6c757d !important;
      }
      .section {
        padding-top: 120px; /* Increased padding to move the section down */
        padding-bottom: 80px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../partials/header.ejs') %>
    <section class="section bg-light" id="about">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h3 class="section-title">
              Welcome To
              <span class="text-custom">Young Africans Technology</span>
            </h3>
            <div class="section-title-border"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row mt-5">
          <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h4 class="font-weight-bold">
              Young Africans Technology, a Nonprofit Coding Academy dedicated to
              providing free coding and Robotics classes to Kid and teenagers.
              <br />
              Our mission is to equip these young minds with valuable skills
              that can open doors to promising careers in the tech industry.
            </h4>
            <p class="text-muted mt-3">
              At Young Africans Technology, we offer comprehensive training to
              kids and teenagers between 10 and 18 years of age in Web and
              mobile app development, basic game development, robotics, and
              basic artificial intelligence.<br />
              Our curriculum includes programming languages such as Python,
              JavaScript, and C++, ensuring our students gain a solid foundation
              in multiple, highly sought-after technologies to prepare them for
              future opportunities.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted mt-3">
              We have a well-structured physical classroom located in Cape Town,
              Khayelitsha Township, where we currently have 36 dedicated
              students.<br />
              Additionally, we offer online programs that include students from
              various countries, such as Nigeria, Ghana, Kenya, Uganda, South
              Africa, Gabon, the USA, the UK, Canada, and Germany.<br />
              This diverse cohort enriches our learning environment and broadens
              the perspectives of all our students.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted mt-3">
              Our programs are supported by volunteer instructors from different
              countries, including the USA, Romania, Ghana, Nigeria, Kenya,
              Uganda, and South Africa, who are dedicated to providing
              high-quality education and mentorship to our students.<br />
              We are also proud to partner with the UCT Developers Society and
              OpenEDG to provide top-tier coding skills and certifications to
              our students.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
